Command: use <skill> [ at <target> ]
Arguments:
  <skill>   is the skill that you want to use. Type 'skills' to see your skills.
            However, most of your skills work automaticly.
  <target>  can be an object or a creature. Not all skills need target.

Examples:
  use kick at ant
  use torch creation

See also 'skill' and 'skills'.
